FROM (
    SELECT `h`.`ID`, `h`.`COMPLETETIME`, `h`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `h`.`CREATETIME`, `h`.`CreationTime`, `h`.`CreatorId`, `h`.`DATA`, `h`.`DeleterId`, `h`.`DeletionTime`, `h`.`DESCRIPTION`, `h`.`ExtraProperties`, `h`.`IsDeleted`, `h`.`LastModificationTime`, `h`.`LastModifierId`, `h`.`NEXTEXECUTION`, `h`.`REFERENCE`, `h`.`STATUS`, `h`.`TENANTID`, `h`.`VERSION`, `h`.`WKDIFINITIONID`, `h0`.`ID` AS `ID0`, `h0`.`COLOR`, `h0`.`ConcurrencyStamp` AS `ConcurrencyStamp0`, `h0`.`CreationTime` AS `CreationTime0`, `h0`.`CreatorId` AS `CreatorId0`, `h0`.`DeleterId` AS `DeleterId0`, `h0`.`DeletionTime` AS `DeletionTime0`, `h0`.`DISCRIPTION`, `h0`.`ExtraProperties` AS `ExtraProperties0`, `h0`.`GROUPID`, `h0`.`ICON`, `h0`.`IsDeleted` AS `IsDeleted0`, `h0`.`LastModificationTime` AS `LastModificationTime0`, `h0`.`LastModifierId` AS `LastModifierId0`, `h0`.`LIMITTIME`, `h0`.`SORTNUMBER`, `h0`.`TENANTID` AS `TENANTID0`, `h0`.`TITLE`, `h0`.`VERSION` AS `VERSION0`, `h0`.`WKDEFINITIONSTATE`
    FROM `HXWKINSTANCES` AS `h`
    INNER JOIN `HXWKDEFINITIONS` AS `h0` ON `h`.`WKDIFINITIONID` = `h0`.`ID`
    WHERE `h`.`ID` = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t`
